<D>__{sunday. river pointerior around noon.}
<A>__{jacey watches through the window as alice returns to the town & country station wagon and puts a few coins into the meter. joan waits impatiently beside the car with susan in hand. as the abbott women walk down the sidewalk (away from the diner), alice glances back and sees jacey smiling at her from the diner window.}
